WEBVTT

00:01:57.580 --> 00:02:02.653
we discovered those gravitational
waves for the first time.

00:02:03.542 --> 00:02:06.066
It's a rather long story.

00:02:06.598 --> 00:02:12.042
It started 1.3 billion years ago.

00:02:13.017 --> 00:02:15.550
A long, long time ago,

00:02:15.574 --> 00:02:18.765
in a galaxy far, far away --

00:02:18.789 --> 00:02:20.582
(Laughter)

00:02:20.606 --> 00:02:26.225
two black holes were revolving
around one another --

00:02:26.249 --> 00:02:29.137
"dancing the tango," I like to say.

00:02:29.161 --> 00:02:30.712
It started slowly,